      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Scott Gasch</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:182px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottgasch\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/f5/Scottgasch.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Scottgasch.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Scott Gasch <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Scott Gasch</b>, <br />\nan American computer scientist, and software engineer at <a href=\"/index.php?title=Google&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Google (page does not exist)\">Google Inc.</a> since 2005, before affiliated with <a href=\"/Microsoft\" title=\"Microsoft\">Microsoft</a>. He holds a B.Sc. in computer science from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Tech\">Virginia Tech</a>.\nScott is author of the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess programs</a> <a href=\"/Monsoon\" title=\"Monsoon\">Monsoon</a> and its multithreaded successor <a href=\"/Typhoon\" title=\"Typhoon\">Typhoon</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Gasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Gasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=20265\">Storing the PV in a search routine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 09, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation\" title=\"Principal Variation\">Principal Variation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=61063\">Q: pawn hash?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 20, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=64838\">razoring?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=72219\">Pawn promotion defense</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 07, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Promotions\" title=\"Promotions\">Promotions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Gasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=172885\">Recapture Extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">Recapture Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=186273\">Parallel search algorithms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=237893\">Checks in the Qsearch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Gasch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 28, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">Check</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Gasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottgasch\">Scott Gasch - Sr. Staff Software Engineer - Google | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wannabe.guru.org/scott/info/\">Scott's homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wannabe.guru.org/scott/hobbies/chess/\">Monsoon/Typhoon Homepage</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Gasch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottgasch\">Scott Gasch - Sr. Staff Software Engineer - Google | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wannabe.guru.org/scott/hobbies/chess/\">Monsoon/Typhoon Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228175901\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!--